<component type="desktop">
    <id>org.mintguide.WebAppReader</id>
    <name>WebAppReader</name>
    <summary>Downloading and viewing websites offline</summary>
    <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
    <project_license>MIT</project_license>
    <developer_name>Sergei Shekin</developer_name>
    <description>
        <p>WebAppReader is a tool for organizing saved websites for offline and even online viewing. Allows you to save
            web pages and entire portals for later viewing without internet access.
        </p>
        <p>It was created taking into account the needs of users who need convenient access to information
            (documentation) at any time.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Downloading and viewing websites offline or online</li>
            <li>Website catalog management</li>
            <li>Category management</li>
            <li>Full website download*</li>
            <li>Partial website download*</li>
        </ul>
        <p>*Not all sources allow downloading their resources.</p>
    </description>
